reviewText: On this DVD, we expected to see Fluffy most of the time, but it didn't work out that way. He's mostly the host of this show, and other comedians do the stand up, with one or two short spotlights for Fluffy. The guest comics used some language and adult comedy, so this one isn't suitable for family viewing. Adults would like it fine. Item arrived in excellent shape, and shipping was fast. Would recommend seller and would buy from again. A+
As like before, stand-up revolution contains 1/2 funny comedians. Though they could not compete with Gabriel Iglesias. ! disc short compare to the last season.

It seems like they spent a lot of time on other projects on this one, and gave less time to the comedians to perform. I like this show, but I want to see more of the comedians, and not as much other stuff.

Great DVD, as usual with Fluffy.  I have bought many of his videos.  I love comedy videos but this is one that you can share with the whole family with no worries of bad words or inappropriate subjects which makes it even better!
Hope there wil be a third season or cartoon down the road. If you like his stand-up, you will like this.
It was ok, not as strong as the first season or his specials, but in the generally same tone as fluffy.  Needs more fluffy!

We absolutely LOVE Fluffy!  Unfortunately, this DVD was more about him opening up an event and emceeing for other not-even-close-to-funny people.  I bought this DVD hoping to see a lot of funny Fluffy, but that was NOT the case.  This is NOT a Fluffy DVD, but mostly a collection of other people trying to break into the business with the help of Fluffy.
